## Troubleshooting Common Errors

| Error | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'seaborn'` | Run `!pip install seaborn` |
| `NameError: name 'sns' is not defined` | Make sure you imported seaborn (`import seaborn as sns`) |
| `KeyError: 'seaborn-v0_8-darkgrid'` | Change to `plt.style.use('ggplot')` or `plt.style.use('default')` |
| Plots not showing | Add `%matplotlib inline` at the very top |
| MCTS takes too long | Reduce iterations from 2000 to 500 or 1000 |

